                            <div class="description">
                                <div class="img"> <img class="rss_img" src="nan"></img> </div>
                                <div class="more"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><div class="contentfulRichText_titleSpacingH3__wUQTI"><h3 class="title_title__DWL5N title_titleSizeS__om4Io title_titleWeightSemibold__RAo21 title_titleFamilyInter__Ra6_Q" id="databases-got-a-makeover">Databases got a makeover</h3></div></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">From clearer names and cleaner tables to simpler settings, gentler visuals, and fewer distractions, databases just got much simpler! The new ‚Äú+ property‚Äù makes naming and picking a property much smoother. You can now group, insert, or rename properties right from the property menu. Web, desktop, mobile‚Äîall refreshed! <a class="InlineTextLink_inlineLink__oN8YM InlineTextLink_colorInherit__oGlTG" href="https://x.com/NotionHQ/status/1935380233265496134" rel="nofollow" target="_self"><span class="InlineTextLink_linkContent__SYI4r">See the full list of updates</span></a>.</p></div><div class="contentfulRichTextLayout_rtSpacingS__fOW8p"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><figure class="mediaWithCaption_figure__Q6RPs"><div class="mediaWithCaption_media__TLfag"><img alt="Databases BeforeAfter" class="next-image contentfulAsset_image__cZ0Nl" data-nimg="1" decoding="async" height="674" loading="lazy" src="https://images.ctfassets.net/spoqsaf9291f/4k4HT89M8G2ZIcnu1WDlBq/8ad02a166d6ec32f55fe33f2139249f6/Databases_BeforeAfter.gif" style="color:transparent" width="900"/></div></figure></div></div> <div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><div class="contentfulRichText_titleSpacingH3__wUQTI"><h3 class="title_title__DWL5N title_titleSizeS__om4Io title_titleWeightSemibold__RAo21 title_titleFamilyInter__Ra6_Q" id="new">New <code class="contentfulRichText_code__RWBxk">Feed</code> view to review content</h3></div></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Like turning your database into a blog feed! Use it to scroll through status updates, user research, bug reports, and more‚Äîthen add comments and emoji reactions. üëÄ </p></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Just add a new view to your database and select <code class="contentfulRichText_code__RWBxk">Feed</code>.</p></div><div class="contentfulRichTextLayout_rtSpacingS__fOW8p"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><figure class="mediaWithCaption_figure__Q6RPs"><div class="mediaWithCaption_media__TLfag"><video class="Video_video__KYz0l Video_videoAspectRatio__qVTeE contentfulAsset_video__OyfPY" height="600" loop="" muted="" playsinline="" preload="none" src="//videos.ctfassets.net/spoqsaf9291f/tBuYJmohXpQ4EtXSapjcH/9c554fc5a3320ec9d3d22528d3366948/FeedView_Students.mp4" style="--video-aspect-ratio:960 / 600" width="960"></video></div></figure></div></div> <div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><div class="contentfulRichText_titleSpacingH3__wUQTI"><h3 class="title_title__DWL5N title_titleSizeS__om4Io title_titleWeightSemibold__RAo21 title_titleFamilyInter__Ra6_Q" id="chat-with-your-database-in-research-mode">Chat with your database in research mode</h3></div></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Now Notion AI can answer extra-complex questions about your databases, drawing info from across properties and any notes inside your database pages. For example, ‚ÄúWhich accounts in @Sales CRM have call notes that mention European data residency?‚Äù</p></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Try it by going to <code class="contentfulRichText_code__RWBxk">Home</code>, selecting the <code class="contentfulRichText_code__RWBxk">Research</code> tab, and @-mention a database in your question.</p></div><div class="contentfulRichTextLayout_rtSpacingS__fOW8p"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><figure class="mediaWithCaption_figure__Q6RPs"><div class="mediaWithCaption_media__TLfag"><img alt="image - 2025-07-10T105650.969" class="next-image contentfulAsset_image__cZ0Nl" data-nimg="1" decoding="async" height="1800" loading="lazy" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F5wwGubpl3t4WzQcloaU6N0%2F896114d6e50bbbae2889a1dda3fb834d%2Fimage_-_2025-07-10T105650.969.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F5wwGubpl3t4WzQcloaU6N0%2F896114d6e50bbbae2889a1dda3fb834d%2Fimage_-_2025-07-10T105650.969.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 1x" style="color:transparent" width="2400"/></div></figure></div></div> <div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><div class="contentfulRichText_titleSpacingH3__wUQTI"><h3 class="title_title__DWL5N title_titleSizeS__om4Io title_titleWeightSemibold__RAo21 title_titleFamilyInter__Ra6_Q" id="database-row-permissions-(coming-soon)">Database row permissions (coming soon)</h3></div></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Notion‚Äôs #2 most requested feature is nearly here! (#1 is offline mode, also <a class="InlineTextLink_inlineLink__oN8YM InlineTextLink_colorInherit__oGlTG" href="https://x.com/ivanhzhao/status/1917945420975841318" rel="nofollow" target="_self"><span class="InlineTextLink_linkContent__SYI4r">coming </span></a>!) You‚Äôll be able to grant permissions by database row. The person assigned to those database pages won‚Äôt be able to see the rest of the database. Stay tuned.</p></div><div class="contentfulRichTextLayout_rtSpacingS__fOW8p"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><figure class="mediaWithCaption_figure__Q6RPs"><div class="mediaWithCaption_media__TLfag"><img alt="db perms" class="next-image contentfulAsset_image__cZ0Nl" data-nimg="1" decoding="async" height="1800" loading="lazy" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F4d1ieP9WoS1G87YebehBRP%2F3f2cef10fe0ad8039e074f6471679102%2Fimage_-_2025-07-10T105656.355.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F4d1ieP9WoS1G87YebehBRP%2F3f2cef10fe0ad8039e074f6471679102%2Fimage_-_2025-07-10T105656.355.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 1x" style="color:transparent" width="2400"/></div></figure></div></div> <div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><div class="contentfulRichText_titleSpacingH3__wUQTI"><h3 class="title_title__DWL5N title_titleSizeS__om4Io title_titleWeightSemibold__RAo21 title_titleFamilyInter__Ra6_Q" id="search-gmail-with-enterprise-search">Search Gmail with Enterprise Search</h3></div></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Have 17,362 messages in your Gmail inbox? Notion AI can help. Search through older archives and new emails to get the latest updates on a project or summarize a long thread. We maintain strict privacy controls, so each user can only see their own inbox. Available on Business and Enterprise plans.</p></div><div class="contentfulRichTextLayout_rtSpacingS__fOW8p"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><figure class="mediaWithCaption_figure__Q6RPs"><div class="mediaWithCaption_media__TLfag"><img alt="Gmail - Tab" class="next-image contentfulAsset_image__cZ0Nl" data-nimg="1" decoding="async" height="2000" loading="lazy" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F3i7KXTygOXvIpjqjoSyV3M%2F4a5cf6ee4747f800a6ec05780e27c0d0%2FGmail_-_Tab.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F3i7KXTygOXvIpjqjoSyV3M%2F4a5cf6ee4747f800a6ec05780e27c0d0%2FGmail_-_Tab.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 1x" style="color:transparent" width="3640"/></div></figure></div></div> <div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><div class="contentfulRichText_titleSpacingH3__wUQTI"><h3 class="title_title__DWL5N title_titleSizeS__om4Io title_titleWeightSemibold__RAo21 title_titleFamilyInter__Ra6_Q" id="‚Ä¶and-search-across-linear">‚Ä¶and search across Linear</h3></div></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Managing projects in Linear? Notion AI can now search those projects and issues‚Äîincluding titles, assignees, creators, and comments. Ask questions like, ‚ÄúWhat blockers are assigned to me this week?‚Äù and get instant answers with citations, all while respecting your Linear permissions. Available on Business and Enterprise plans.</p></div><div class="contentfulRichTextLayout_rtSpacingS__fOW8p"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><figure class="mediaWithCaption_figure__Q6RPs"><div class="mediaWithCaption_media__TLfag"><img alt="Linear - tab" class="next-image contentfulAsset_image__cZ0Nl" data-nimg="1" decoding="async" height="2000" loading="lazy" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F28icEXv04vFDaY9FJY1Zk9%2F01810dc062dc9257c216f7fa2ee414e9%2FLinear_-_tab.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F28icEXv04vFDaY9FJY1Zk9%2F01810dc062dc9257c216f7fa2ee414e9%2FLinear_-_tab.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 1x" style="color:transparent" width="3640"/></div></figure></div></div> <div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><div class="contentfulRichText_titleSpacingH3__wUQTI"><h3 class="title_title__DWL5N title_titleSizeS__om4Io title_titleWeightSemibold__RAo21 title_titleFamilyInter__Ra6_Q" id="build-with-replit-manage-with-notion">Build with Replit, manage with Notion</h3></div></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Vibe coding continues to amaze us. Now you can connect your apps and websites to a Notion database to manage all the content: visual assets, posts, and tasks. Check out this Replit <a class="InlineTextLink_inlineLink__oN8YM InlineTextLink_colorInherit__oGlTG" href="https://x.com/mattppal/status/1927364391281799504" rel="nofollow" target="_self"><span class="InlineTextLink_linkContent__SYI4r">demo</span></a>.</p></div><div class="contentfulRichTextLayout_rtSpacingS__fOW8p"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><figure class="mediaWithCaption_figure__Q6RPs"><div class="mediaWithCaption_media__TLfag"><img alt="Replit" class="next-image contentfulAsset_image__cZ0Nl" data-nimg="1" decoding="async" height="1800" loading="lazy" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F4fGa3liSBas1cpxtlMsrFh%2F2d90bc38837af8ed39854ef5e640ec31%2FReplit.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F4fGa3liSBas1cpxtlMsrFh%2F2d90bc38837af8ed39854ef5e640ec31%2FReplit.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 1x" style="color:transparent" width="2400"/></div></figure></div></div> <div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><div class="contentfulRichText_titleSpacingH3__wUQTI"><h3 class="title_title__DWL5N title_titleSizeS__om4Io title_titleWeightSemibold__RAo21 title_titleFamilyInter__Ra6_Q" id="importing-csvs-just-got-a-lot-cleaner">Importing CSVs just got a lot cleaner</h3></div></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Now you can select which Notion Property Type you want to use for each CSV column, making imports so much tidier! Simply upload and create a new database or merge your CSV with an existing database.</p></div><div class="contentfulRichTextLayout_rtSpacingS__fOW8p"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><figure class="mediaWithCaption_figure__Q6RPs"><div class="mediaWithCaption_media__TLfag"><img alt="image - 2025-07-10T105719.630" class="next-image contentfulAsset_image__cZ0Nl" data-nimg="1" decoding="async" height="1800" loading="lazy" src="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F4MTm84U7shCbPKsqOrNFWY%2F4768025540e89378c9f3c7d8f0678491%2Fimage_-_2025-07-10T105719.630.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75" srcset="/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fimages.ctfassets.net%2Fspoqsaf9291f%2F4MTm84U7shCbPKsqOrNFWY%2F4768025540e89378c9f3c7d8f0678491%2Fimage_-_2025-07-10T105719.630.png&amp;w=3840&amp;q=75 1x" style="color:transparent" width="2400"/></div></figure></div></div> <div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><div class="contentfulRichText_titleSpacingH3__wUQTI"><h3 class="title_title__DWL5N title_titleSizeS__om4Io title_titleWeightSemibold__RAo21 title_titleFamilyInter__Ra6_Q" id="lots-of-improvements!">Lots of improvements!</h3></div></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><ul class="contentfulRichText_list__89IEM"><li class="contentfulRichText_listItem___Swmu"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Databases are way <a class="InlineTextLink_inlineLink__oN8YM InlineTextLink_colorInherit__oGlTG" href="https://x.com/NotionHQ/status/1935737823707165156" rel="nofollow" target="_self"><span class="InlineTextLink_linkContent__SYI4r">easier to use on mobile</span></a>. Tap, view, edit, or create filters with a couple flicks of your thumb.</p></div></li><li class="contentfulRichText_listItem___Swmu"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Manage any Notion database in Notion Calendar if it includes dates. Just click into the view and select </p></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE"><code class="contentfulRichText_code__RWBxk">Open in Calendar</code>. Great for tracking deadlines.</p></div></li><li class="contentfulRichText_listItem___Swmu"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Search your PDFs in Notion, Google Drive, SharePoint and OneDrive with Enterprise Search!</p></div></li><li class="contentfulRichText_listItem___Swmu"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Google Drive AI Connector can now search across more file types: .docx, pptx, xlsx, csv, and PDFs.</p></div></li><li class="contentfulRichText_listItem___Swmu"><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE">Organization owners can now place users under <a class="InlineTextLink_inlineLink__oN8YM InlineTextLink_colorInherit__oGlTG" href="https://www.notion.com/help/legal-holds" rel="nofollow" target="_self"><span class="InlineTextLink_linkContent__SYI4r">legal hold</span></a> and preserve all the docs they‚Äôve created, edited, or viewed‚Äîpreventing deletion of important files.</p></div></li></ul></div><div class="contentfulRichText_bodyLimit__F5GOU" style="--rich-text-limit-max-width:none"><p class="contentfulRichText_paragraph___hjRE"></p></div></div>
